name: FDataRegistrySourceToAdd
doc: Defines which source assets to add and conditions for adding

RegistryToAddTo: Name of the registry to add to
AssetPriority: Priority to use when adding to the registry.  Higher priorities are searched first
DataTableToAdd: Link to the data table to add to the registry
CurveTableToAdd: Link to the curve table to add to the registry
bClientSource: Should this component be added for clients
bServerSource: Should this component be added on servers
